.Sh DESCRIPTION
The virtqueue functions provide an API into the most important VirtIO abstraction.
.Pp
The
.Fn virtqueue_alloc
function allocates a virtqueue using
.Xr malloc 9 ,
and assigning it the
.Xr device 9
dev.
Conversely,
.Fn virtqueue_free
frees the virtqueue.
